You must install the electronic Help to view Help content here. Learn about printer use, features, troubleshooting, notices, environmental, regulatory, and support information from the electronic Help.
You can install the electronic Help from the HP software CD or the support website:
To install from the HP software CD, insert the CD, and then begin installing the software.
To install from the support website, visit hp.com/support, and then download the “Full Feature Software and Drivers” software.
When you see the screen listing recommended software, make sure the “[prodName] Help” option is selected.
